      "date": "2015-03-16 15:18:36.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAndreas, I don't know the customer's workload that gets a node into the state where the shrinker performance becomes an issue. But they do reproduce it with regularity. My intent is to give them this patch so they can measure what effect it has. I suspect there's more at play here than lu_cache_shrink. We're just whittling away at the problem bit by bit. I'll update the header with more info when I submit the next version of the patch.",
